    "block_type": "text",
    "order_index": 1,
    "data": {
      "content_translations": {
        "nl": "Onze villa is gebouwd in 2018 en met liefde ingericht door lokale ambachtslieden. Elke kamer combineert traditionele Caribische details met moderne luxe.",
        "en": "Our villa was built in 2018 and lovingly designed by local craftspeople. Every room blends traditional Caribbean details with modern luxury."
